Vanessa Angel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vanessa_Angel 0 Vanessa Madeline Angel (born 10 November 1966) is an English-American actress and former model. She played the role of Lisa on the television series Weird Science. She is also known for her role as Claudia in the film Kingpin.
